Pre-Ship:
* Make sure there are no remaining "TODO" and "FIXME" in the code
* Check for (replaceable) calls to fatalError()
* Update dependencies in settings

Post-Ship:
* After the version goes live, make a branch. There doesn't necessarily have to be only one commit on that branch, just no additional features

